N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6211.8 - Applicability

State Regulations

This part shall apply in relation to any election at which
early voting is held pursuant to title VI of article 8 of the election law as
enacted by chapter 6 of the laws of 2019. Notes
